1. Molim te, *napusti* moju sobu. (Please, *leave* my room.)
2. Odlučio sam *napustiti* posao i tražiti nešto bolje. (I've decided to *quit* my job and look for something better.)
3. Ako ne budeš radio bolje, moraću da te *napustim*. (If you don't perform better, I'll have to *abandon* you.)
4. Jutros je *napustila* svoj stan bez ikakvog objašnjenja. (This morning, she *left* her apartment without any explanation.)
5. Njegov otac ga je *napustio* kada je bio jako mlad. (His father *abandoned* him when he was very young.)
6. Da li ćeš *napustiti* ovaj grad ili ostati? (Will you *leave* this city or stay?)
7. Učenici su *napustili* školu nakon što je završio poslednji čas. (The students *left* school after the last class ended.)
8. Trebalo bi da *napustite* ovaj restoran, jer već zatvaraju. (You should *leave* this restaurant, as they are closing already.)
9. Nakon nekoliko meseci, odlučili su *napustiti* svoj plan putovanja. (After a few months, they decided to *abandon* their travel plan.)
10. Koliko puta si već *napustio* ovaj projekat? (How many times have you already *left* this project?)